	("zh_Hans_CN",	"LOC_BELIEF_JUST_WAR_DL_DESCRIPTION",					"宗教武装单位和宗教单位在平坦地形+1[ICON_Movement]速,所有单位劫掠区域和改良时+50[ICON_FAITH]鸽。"),
	("en_US",		"LOC_UNIT_WARRIOR_MONK_DESCRIPTION",				"Religious armed units, which cost more than militants, have one use time to advance the construction progress of the District_Holy  by 20%.Can only be purchased with [ICON_FAITH] Faith in city with Temple or Church."),
	("zh_Hans_CN",	"LOC_UNIT_WARRIOR_MONK_DESCRIPTION",				"比武装教徒造价更高的宗教武装单位,拥有一次使用次数来推进圣地20%的建造进度。只能在有寺庙或教堂的城市通过 [ICON_FAITH] 信仰购买。"),
